5. Transition to On‚ÄëChain Governance

While our current governance model is implemented off‚Äëchain via Discord, our long-term vision is to transition to a fully integrated DApp on the Cosmos network. This migration will:
	‚Ä¢	Record All Actions On‚ÄëChain: Enhancing transparency and security.
	‚Ä¢	Maintain Non-Transferability: Ensuring that Soulbound NFTs remain permanently linked to the original owner.
	‚Ä¢	Integrate a Unified Dashboard: Providing real-time monitoring of proposals, votes, and rewards.

‚∏ª

6. Conclusion

The off‚Äëchain governance workflow on Discord establishes a dynamic, time‚Äëbased, and ethically grounded decision-making process for the D.ream D.Truth Protocol. Through our detailed emoji voting system, structured daily cycle, and robust moderation process, we ensure that credibility and governance weight are directly linked to verified, quality contributions. This model sets the stage for a future migration to an on‚Äëchain Cosmos DApp, where all interactions will be recorded with full transparency.

